{"tid":2077774,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"證實將設市府版港澳辦公室 柯文哲：務實做事、不是騙選票","createTime":"2020-06-24T13:58:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T17:58:20.000Z","uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"51473fe3728a5b22e75930bbddfc7c752625ca03","tid":2077774,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T13:58:47.000Z","msg":"證實將設市府版港澳辦公室 柯文哲：務實做事、不是騙選票<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3207426\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3207426&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPqDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=ca589d21\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3207426&h=6dddde19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3207426</a><br />\n<br />\n〔記者沈佩瑤／台北報導〕為因應港版國安法，陸委會日前公布「香港人道援助關懷行動專案」，「台港服務交流辦公室」將於7月1日正式營運。柯市府不讓中央專美於前，近期也悄悄由副市長蔡炳坤擔綱負責人，將成立北市府版「港澳專案辦公室」。市長柯文哲今上午受訪證實此事，但強調自己的施政風格一向是務實，要提供香港人必要和所需協助，不要打嘴砲，自己不是來騙選票的。<br />\n<br />\n柯文哲上午主持「北市高中職生振興加碼方案」記者會後受訪，談及將成立北市府版「港澳專案辦公室」，柯強調自己的施政風格一向是務實，香港問題從去年鬧到現在，他的態度從頭到尾一致：務實處理香港問題，給香港人必要和他們需要的協助，包括就學、就業、投資。<br />\n<br />\n柯指出，他認為很多香港人想移民或是到其他地方投資，台北若不做好準備，就會全部跑到新加坡去，所以不要打嘴砲，而是要務實的工作。<br />\n<br />\n所以針對香港局勢發展，柯表示，由副市長蔡炳坤當召集人，組成專案小組，對於香港人來台灣的就學、就業、定居、置產、投資等進行跨局處會議，並準備一個網站，把港人需要的所有資訊都放上去，「政治上務實的做事，我們不是騙選票」。"},{"pid":"5ce692aa99d3a56cd92dfcbeff016b32075f1dba","tid":2077774,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T14:00:29.000Z","msg":"中華民國台北市香港區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"245cd4117205e629cfe12aedb908a34845f0205d","tid":2077774,"uid":335434,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T14:23:01.000Z","msg":"你唔好搞到變北京果個「港澳辦」咁就得喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2efaac5f1dedd704d708b6a87ef62a9e16410913","tid":2077774,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T14:37:53.000Z","msg":"鬥黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6deda3676397f9326e932beba38f61f9d5688c34","tid":2077774,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T14:49:34.000Z","msg":"信唔過"},{"pid":"50d4b9957b3383cbc928973304af8f59066af13e","tid":2077774,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T14:50:32.000Z","msg":"歡迎鬥黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea71c33e372b6fda792f54dd5f14dc06042a21a3","tid":2077774,"uid":105298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T14:52:09.000Z","msg":"全球都想食香港個肥豬肉<br />\n係得支那唔要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"494929d74d1536a32a1b3b052a2e510fe8ddfcf3","tid":2077774,"uid":170244,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T14:57:30.000Z","msg":"搵佢地幫手,<br />\n佢地分分鐘將你發夢嘅證據送中,<br />\n再用各種理由踢你返香港,甚至送去大陸<br />\n<br />\n因為而家嘅柯文哲,做嘅野同十一哥差唔多"},{"pid":"680030b75fbee0766d23623656ac189ac122e460","tid":2077774,"uid":21493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ce692aa99d3a56cd92dfcbeff016b32075f1dba","tid":2077774,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T14:00:29.000Z","msg":"中華民國台北市香港區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T15:01:28.000Z","msg":"台北唔係都咩?"},{"pid":"0098ed66900114299c31d8c5ed3e32d034b0bf3e","tid":2077774,"uid":311198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"494929d74d1536a32a1b3b052a2e510fe8ddfcf3","tid":2077774,"uid":17024